text: Jeong Dong-gu (born 20 March 1942) is a South Korean wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle lightweight at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of South Korea Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Wrestlers at the 1962 Asian Games Category:Asian Games competitors for South Korea
